
'''''The Cursed Ones''''' ni filime yo mu Bwongereza ya 2015 yayobowe na Nana Obiri Yeboah ikorwa na Nicholas K. Lory<ref>The Cursed Ones - Film at Lincoln Center <nowiki>https://www.filmlinc.org</nowiki> › films › the-cursed-ones</ref> . Amashusho yumwimerere yanditswe na Maximilian Claussen <ref>The Cursed Ones | African Film Festival, Inc. <nowiki>https://africanfilmny.org</nowiki> › films › the-cursed-ones</ref>. Iyi filime ivuga amateka y’umunyamakuru wacitse intege ndetse n’umupasitori ukiri muto ufite ibitekerezo<ref>Review: "The Cursed Ones" and the Burden of History <nowiki>https://www.cinemaescapist.com</nowiki> › 2018/02 › cursed-on...</ref>, urwanira kubohora umukobwa uregwa ubupfumu mu maboko ya gahunda yononekaye n’imiziririzo hagati muri Afurika y’iburengerazuba<ref>The Cursed Ones - movie: watch streaming online - JustWatch <nowiki>https://www.justwatch.com</nowiki> › movie › the-cursed-ones</ref> .

Filime yahawe ibihembo 3 bya African Movie Academy Awards mu 2016 ''kubuyobozi bwiza'', ''Sinema nziza'', hamwe nubushakashatsi ''bwiza''<ref>The Cursed Ones | Tickets for film 21/12 – 30/12/2020, Polska <nowiki>https://goout.net</nowiki> › Venues › Streamed event</ref> .  Yatowe mu bihembo 13 bya AMAA byose hamwe, bituma iba filime yatowe kurusha izindi mu 2016. <ref>http://ama-awards.com/v/index.php/news/540-press-release-breaking-news-amaa-announces-2016-nomination-list</ref>

